Package: libcmaesr
Title: R Interface to 'libcmaes'
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bernd", "Bischl", , "bernd_bischl@gmx.net", role = c("cre", "aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6002-6980")),
    person("Martin", "Binder", , "mlr.developer@mb706.com", role = "aut")
  )
Copyright: See inst/COPYRIGHTS for 'libcmaes' copyright details
Description: A lightweight R interface to the 'libcmaes' C++ library for
    Covariance Matrix Adaptation Evolution Strategy (CMA-ES). It allows for the
    optimization of black-box functions using the CMA-ES algorithm and its
    variants. Includes a bundled copy of 'libcmaes' (LGPL-3+); see
    'inst/COPYRIGHTS'. Requires system 'Eigen3' headers.
License: LGPL-3
URL: https://github.com/mlr-org/libcmaesr
BugReports: https://github.com/mlr-org/libcmaesr/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 3.6.0)
Imports:
    checkmate,
    mlr3misc,
    stats
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/testthat/parallel: false
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-US
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: C++11, Eigen3 headers (>= 3.3), pkg-config or CMake
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE, load = "installed")
